---
---
<section class="trust" id="trust">
  <div class="trust-inner">
    <div class="trust-header">
      <h2 class="trust-title">
        Built for the kind of work <em>that gets audited.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="trust-sub">
        Auditors, lawyers, and HR investigations don't get to be casual about data.
        Neither do we.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="trust-grid">

      <div class="trust-cell">
        <div class="trust-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-cell-body">
          <div class="trust-cell-title">SOC 2 Type II</div>
          <div class="trust-cell-text">Independently audited. Annual recertification. Report available under NDA. SOC 1 in progress.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-cell">
        <div class="trust-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-cell-body">
          <div class="trust-cell-title">Seven-year audit playback</div>
          <div class="trust-cell-text">Every interview, every system event, replayable for seven years. Built for the long retention windows your industry requires.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-cell">
        <div class="trust-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-cell-body">
          <div class="trust-cell-title">Disclosure &amp; consent</div>
          <div class="trust-cell-text">Every interviewee sees an AI-interview disclosure before they begin. Their consent is timestamped and stored alongside the transcript.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-cell">
        <div class="trust-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-cell-body">
          <div class="trust-cell-title">Your data is yours</div>
          <div class="trust-cell-text">We don't train models on your interviews. We don't sell your data. Period. Deletion on request, full export anytime.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-cell">
        <div class="trust-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-cell-body">
          <div class="trust-cell-title">Encrypted end to end</div>
          <div class="trust-cell-text">AES-256 at rest. TLS 1.3 in transit. Key management via dedicated KMS, with optional customer-managed keys for enterprise.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="trust-cell">
        <div class="trust-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 010 20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 000 20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-cell-body">
          <div class="trust-cell-title">Data residency on request</div>
          <div class="trust-cell-text">US, EU, or APAC region pinning available for enterprise customers. GDPR-compliant by default. BIPA-aware proctoring. HIPAA-ready paths for clinical and HR work.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="trust-footnote">
      Read more in our <a href="#">security &amp; compliance documentation</a>,
      review our <a href="#">subprocessor list</a>,
      or talk to our team about your specific requirements.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section.trust {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    background: var(--paper-cool);
    padding: clamp(80px, 12vh, 140px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 56px);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  section.trust::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 0%, rgba(29,53,87,0.05), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 90% 100%, rgba(29,53,87,0.04), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .trust-inner {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }

  .trust-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto clamp(48px, 7vh, 72px);
  }

  h2.trust-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.6vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  h2.trust-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .trust-sub {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.4vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 22px;
  }

  .trust-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .trust-cell {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 24px 26px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .trust-cell:hover {
    border-color: var(--ink-faint);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .trust-mark {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .trust-mark svg {
    width: 18px; height: 18px;
    stroke: currentColor; fill: none; stroke-width: 2;
  }

  .trust-cell-body { flex: 1; }
  .trust-cell-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .trust-cell-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  .trust-footnote {
    margin-top: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .trust-footnote a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-soft);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .trust-footnote a:hover { text-decoration-color: var(--accent); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .trust-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
